---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Mechanistic Interpretability | Harutyun Harry Ilanyan">
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Neural Network Interpretability Suite</h1>
    
    <div class="alert alert-secondary mb-8">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-current shrink-0 w-6 h-6">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
      </svg>
      <span>This research project is exploring cutting-edge interpretability techniques.</span>
    </div>

    <h2>Project Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Comprehensive tools for analyzing the internal workings of neural networks, focusing on feature representations, 
      decision processes, and mechanistic understanding of model behaviors. This research aims to enhance AI transparency 
      through detailed analysis of model components.
    </p>

    <h2>Research Objectives</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Develop tools for analyzing neural network internals</li>
      <li>Understand feature representations and their evolution</li>
      <li>Map decision-making processes in deep learning models</li>
      <li>Create visualization tools for model interpretability</li>
      <li>Build mechanistic understanding of transformer architectures</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Technical Stack</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6 not-prose">
      <div class="badge badge-primary">Python</div>
      <div class="badge badge-secondary">Transformers</div>
      <div class="badge badge-accent">Interpretability</div>
      <div class="badge badge-info">Visualization</div>
      <div class="badge badge-success">Analysis</div>
    </div>

    <h2>Research Impact</h2>
    <p>
      This research contributes to the broader goal of making AI systems more transparent and trustworthy by providing 
      insights into how neural networks process information and make decisions.
    </p>

    <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8 not-prose">
      <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-outline">‚Üê Back to Projects</a>
      <a href="mailto:harry_ila@berkeley.edu" class="btn btn-primary">Contact for Collaboration</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>